Package org.eclipse.collections.impl.tuple.primitive

Class PrimitiveTuples

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.collections.impl.tuple.primitive.PrimitiveTuples
public final class PrimitiveTuples extends Object
This class should be used to create instances of object/primitive, primitive/primitive and primitive/object pairs.
